quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Did you not see into or ponder O Muhammad how Allah your Creator, dealt with the expedition which included the elephant in their train"
  105,2,Did He not make their strategy as well as tactics simply vain
  105,3,He overwhelmed them with throngs of birds coming in very large flights
  105,4,"Striking them with clay stones, spreading among them an epidemic"
  105,5,Until they became like the stubbles left over in a field that has been reaped